pt-p710bt-label-gui (0.2.0-2) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Preview height dimension now shows the physical tape width (e.g. 12 mm)
    with the printable area drawn inset; non-printable bands are shaded.
  * Wider minimum preview width — empty/short labels stay horizontal.
  * Copies with auto-cut now print as N separate jobs so the cutter fires
    between each label (previously printed as one long strip).
  * Font picker replaced with a modal dialog showing live samples in each
    font face (Hebrew samples for Hebrew fonts) and a filter box.

