pt-p710bt-label-gui (0.2.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Release 0.2.0 — Label tab UX overhaul.
    - Tabbed UI (Label / Batch / Device / Fonts).
    - Soft Qt-rendered preview with "Exact (pixel-accurate)" toggle.
    - Horizontal preview with dimension arrows showing tape height and
