pt-p710bt-label-gui (0.1.0-7) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Preview reworked: label is now drawn as a horizontal strip at the true
    label width (no square minimum), with dimension arrows on the left and
    bottom showing tape height and label length in mm.
  * New "Fill tape height" option (default OFF). Default auto-sizing is now
    conservative (~60% of tape height) instead of always filling.

